So, let's start from the small to the big.

00:03:27.599 --> 00:03:31.699
So on the iPhone, we have the iPhone Contacts application.

00:03:31.699 --> 00:03:35.109
On Mac OS X, we have the Address Book application.

00:03:35.110 --> 00:03:40.160
And new in Mac OS X Snow Leopard,
we have the Address Book Server.

